para_trans: Regarding sanction of Sub-Centre at Mauje Banpuri, Taluka Atpadi, District Sangli.
Government Decision No: Sub-Collector-2024 / P.No. 183 / Health-4
Read: - Letter No. of Joint Director, Health Services, Mumbai: Go to No. AASE / Room-7A / T-9 / Banpuri / Upakay / Manzoor / Sangli / 2117-19/2024, D. Letter of 27.05.2024.
Preamble: - The matter of sanctioning a Sub-Centre at Mauje Banpuri, Taluka Atpadi, District Sangli.
It was under the consideration of the government. The following decisions are being taken in this regard:
Government Decision: - As a special case for sanction of Sub-Centre at Mauje Banpuri, Taluka Atpadi, District Sangli
It is being approved by the government.
The decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra's www.maharashtra.gov.in website.
